  "title": "Procurement Operations Executive (SAP)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible for timely and accurately raising purchase requisitions  in SAP MM Purchasing upon receipt of approved memo and work order.</li><li>Responsible for timely and accurately performing GRs (Goods Receipt) upon receipt of invoice and approval from authorized leads.</li><li>Ensure that auditable records are kept for each purchase requisition raised.</li><li>Assist in tracking and cross referencing of purchase requisitions and POs for investigative reasons.</li><li>Assist in the reconciliation of purchase requisitions, POs, and project budgets.</li><li>Adhere to the team’s purchase requisition raising process and escalate any breaches.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>3 to 5 years in a similar role.</li><li>Prior expertise at using SAP Material Management (MM) module would be a bonus.</li><li>Excellent written and verbal communications.</li><li>Ability to interact at a professional level.</li><li>Basic understanding of book-keeping and accounting</li><li>Attention to detail.</li><li>Proficient at Excel (Pivot tables, vlookups).</li></ul>",
